    dc:description "Figure 1. Digital Photo-illustration. Habitus, dorsal aspect. A Hyboptera angulicollis Chaudoir, female, ADP 052729 B Hyboptera biolat Erwin & Henry, sp. n., female, ADP 007398." ;
